en: There's a villain in our waters! Help me deal with it.
I have a large order for oars. And a frigate sank nearby. And people escape on boats... With oars... Do you understand?
Lovers of wild recreation are blocking our trade routes with their rafts.  We will gladly pay for a couple of holes in their transport!
The damned aristocrats on the neighboring islands are always having fun on their yachts! That would intimidate them. With a fatal outcome...
An imperial frigate stood nearby. He ruins the whole business. Flood it! I won't be in debt!
A gang of poachers is fishing in our waters in defiance of all treaties. Sink their boats before they destroy the entire bay. For this I will give you a good sum!
Competitors from a neighboring trading company dared to do business in our territory. Your task is to drive away these insolent people. Give them a hard time!
Smugglers in their boats scare fishermen and spoil their catch. If you sink their ships you will give the fishermen their jobs back and I will reward you generously. Ready to take it on?
Heavy fog shrouds the bay at night. This ship is terrorizing the entire coast. Interferes with trade and frightens sailors. If you can send him to the bottom I will reward you generously!
Sink the rafts of our enemies!
Send the ships of the empire to the bottom!
Sink the empire's frigate looking for you
Now I can sleep peacefully! Here is your reward. Do you take it?
Your boat has sunk... Steal a new ship?
You must be logged in to view the leaderboard
Now we can safely pass through the reefs. Want to go further?
Dangerous reefs ahead! Without a map we'll be overwhelmed right away! Come back with the map.
Congratulations on completing the game! Come join us in the next updates!
To swim move your finger across the display
Hand over your loot and upgrade your ship in the bay
Booty! Swim closer! Your team will do everything themselves!
It's worth looking for a map from the locals...
Here you can hand over your loot
Here you can patch up the ship
